## Phase 1: Branch & Config Verification [AUTO]

1. Run `git checkout -b eds-migration` to create the migration branch.
2. Read `gatsby-config.js` and verify it has a `pathPrefix`. Report the path prefix and navigation structure found.

## CHECKPOINT A: Google Sheets Setup [MANUAL]

Pause and instruct the engineer to:

1. Add path prefix `{PATH_PREFIX}` to the **devsitepaths** spreadsheet:
   - Stage: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1GqZ6QJwOhSG-beyd0nIEJ_cHd5PGBTghsqhbTM9nqMs/edit?usp=sharing
   - Prod: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1V_mVmnlREE-QgCM8XA2VNXtRhoTlrFFSCF3Wh_8-4ig/edit?gid=0#gid=0
   - Publish to EDS if not already existing.
2. Verify path prefix exists in **product-index-map** spreadsheet:
   - Stage: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12avDPZeNzR9yLwf9Z-Obv7lzqj96c9glvT3U62aYxeE/edit?gid=0#gid=0
   - Prod: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qmy0ma2wmWDIyU1p1tW0a45i5JnbhEAbUOfRb0lv4rE/edit?gid=0#gid=0
   - Publish to EDS if not already existing.

Use `AskQuestion` with options: "Completed" / "Skip (already done)" / "Need help". Only proceed when engineer confirms.

